description: Defines the Match entity class for a resume-job matching application, representing a match with associated data such as user ID, resume ID, job ID, score, analysis ID, and creation timestamp.

classes.name: Match
classes.description: Entity class representing a match between a resume and a job, including scoring and metadata.

methods.name: getId
methods.description: Returns the unique identifier of the match.

methods.name: getUserId
methods.description: Returns the user ID associated with the match.

methods.name: getResumeId
methods.description: Returns the resume ID linked to the match.

methods.name: getJobId
methods.description: Returns the job ID linked to the match.

methods.name: getAnalysisId
methods.description: Returns the analysis ID related to the match.

methods.name: getCreatedAt
methods.description: Returns the timestamp when the match was created.

methods.name: setUserId
methods.description: Sets the user ID associated with the match.

methods.name: setResumeId
methods.description: Sets the resume ID linked to the match.

methods.name: setJobId
methods.description: Sets the job ID linked to the match.

methods.name: setAnalysisId
methods.description: Sets the analysis ID related to the match.

methods.name: setCreatedAt
methods.description: Sets the creation timestamp of the match.
